# 將數據資料存入變數中
# 0->Pitching, 1->Batting , 2->Forehand, 3->Backhand, 4->Dribbling, 5->Shooting,
# 6->Underhand Serve, 7->Overhead Serve, 8->Forehand Serve, 9->Backhand Serve
